    "syllabus": "Week週次\n\nContent & Class Schedule (教學進度)\n\n1\n\nIntroduction, Overview, & Basic Mathematics\n\n2\n\nGeometrical (Ray) Optics & Image Formation\n\n3\n\nMatrix Optics (I)\n\n4\n\nMatrix Optics (II)\n\n5\n\nMatrix Optics (III): General Optical Imaging Systems\n\n6\n\nBasic Mathematics of Wave Propagation\n\n7\n\nPlane-wave, Spherical Wave, and Cylindrical Wave\n\n8\n\nFresnel Reflection, Equations, and Applications (I)\n\n9\n\nMid-Term Exam (期中測驗評量)\n\n10\n\nFresnel Reflection, Equations, and Applications (II)\n\n11\n\nGaussian Beam Optics (I)\n\n12\n\nGaussian Beam Optics (II)\n\n13\n\nGaussian Beam Transformation\n\n14\n\nOptical Resonators\n\n15\n\nCoherence & Dispersion\n\n16\n\nInterference of 2 Plane-waves\n\n17\n\nOptical Interferometers\n\n18\n\nFinal Exam (期末測驗評量)",
